#: ../../preinstall.rst:168
msgid ""
"**Optimus:** At this time there is no switching support between the two "
"graphics adapters provided by Optimus. Optimus implementations vary, so "
"|trueos| may or may not be able to successfully load a graphics driver on "
"hardware. If a blank screen shows after installation, check the BIOS to see "
"if it has an option to disable one of the graphics adapters or to set "
"*discrete* mode. If the BIOS does not provide a *discrete* mode, |trueos| "
"defaults to the 3D Intel driver and disables NVIDIA. This will change in the"
" future when the NVIDIA driver supports Optimus."
msgstr ""

#: ../../preinstall.rst:183
msgid ""
"|trueos| has built-in support for most wireless networking cards. |trueos| "
"automatically detects available wireless networks for supported wireless "
"devices. Verify the device is supported by clicking the :guilabel:`Hardware "
"Compatibility` icon within the installer. If it is an external wireless "
"device, insert it before running the installer."
