#: ../../preinstall.rst:189
msgid ""
"Certain Broadcom devices, typically found in less expensive laptops, are "
"buggy and can have lockups when in *DMA* mode. If the device freezes, try "
"switching to *PIO* mode in the BIOS. Alternately, add "
":command:`hw.bwn.usedma=0` to :file:`/boot/loader.conf` and reboot to see if"
" anything changes."
