#: ../../preinstall.rst:107
msgid ""
"Check the `FreeBSD Hardware Notes "
"<https://www.freebsd.org/releases/11.0R/hardware.html>`_ to ensure your "
"system hardware is supported before installing |trueos|. Another good option"
" is to start the installer and click the :guilabel:`Hardware Compatibility` "
