#~ msgid ""
#~ "Like many open source operating systems, TrueOS® uses `X.org "
#~ "<https://www.x.org/wiki/>`_ drivers for graphics support. TrueOS® will "
#~ "automatically detect the optimal video settings for supported video drivers."
