#~ msgid "Support for the major graphic vendors is as follows:"
#~ msgstr ""

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**NVIDIA:** 3D acceleration on NVIDIA is provided by native FreeBSD drivers."
#~ " If an NVIDIA video card is detected, an \"nVidia settings\" icon will be "
#~ "added to \"Browse Applications\" for managing NVIDIA settings."
